description: For sale: $564,900. First time offered! This stunning Trout Lake home has so much to offer - inside and out. description: Recently sold: $105,750. Fantastic move-in ready home all spiffed up and ready to find a new owner.  This home has all new flooring, fresh paint, updated kitchen, newer natural gas furnace & windows. Updated electric with GFI breakers and new LED lighting.  Big entry leads you to the updated kitchen w/new counter tops and large pantry.  Nice size dining room opens to the spacious living room which then opens to the front porch where you can sit and enjoy views of Longyear Park and Trout Lake.  One bedroom is attached to the full bath with charming clawfoot tub.  The basement has been cleaned and painted and has an extra bonus room and ¾ bath.  You'll love the 2 car oversized garage w/its new doors & opener.  The driveway has been dug up and class 5 added plus there's a nice patio area where you can have your BBQ & patio set.  Great location near Trout Lake, park and schools.  What more can you ask for!
